    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like a \"step toward something else\" though. it just feels empty. like there's nothing left to rebuild. there isn't even a foundation anymore. i'm just... a shell. you can't rebuild something that's already gone. it's just a hollow space where a person used to be.",
